4️⃣ Control Plane vs Data Plane
Service	Control Plane	Data Plane
EBS	Create Volume, Attach/Detach, Snapshot	Block read/write operations
EFS	Create file system, Create mount targets	NFS read/write traffic
S3	Create bucket, Lifecycle policies, Bucket policies	PUT/GET/DELETE object operations
